td.div: English: OADG 109A, a Japanese keyboard layout in Microsoft Windows.
日本語: Microsoft Windowsで使われる日本語キーボード配列（OADG 109A型）。
한국어: 마이크로소프트 윈도에서 사용되는 일본어 키보드 배열(OADG 109A형).
Bahasa Melayu: OADG 109A, sejenis lakaran papan kekunci bahasa Jepun dalam Microsoft Windows.

tr.td: Varies by versions. (The first version: August 8, 2006)

tr.td: I adjusted positions and shapes of some characters, and added auxiliary boxes and circles.
I changed the color of the hankaku/zenkaku key and the enter key into grey because they are not character keys.
Modify "Alt Gr" key to right "Alt" key, exchange location of "tilde" and "caret" in the key.
Japanese keyboard layout (incomplete). SVG version of en:Image:Basicjapanesekeyboard-notfinished.jpg, based on Image:KB United States.svg. Category:Keyboard layouts
